":"Leadership in Data Science","key":"uLaXbup2cv"}],"url":"/collaboration/leadership","internal":true,"dataUrl":"/collaboration.leadership.json","key":"qwC38ugM3X"},{"type":"text","value":" chapters, we have already discussed in-depth how we can manage a new online community and build healthy leadership for a team.\nTherefore, in this subchapter, we have listed a few reminders of tasks that are specifically important for managing distributed teams.","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1},"end":{"line":4,"column":1}},"key":"dJLk3yUJlT"}],"key":"cZLNNtQhZ3"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Set clear expectations for the team members about the project and their roles and responsibilities.","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"QEC8KmwLjs"}],"key":"hypoq3sIPD"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Help establish all modes of communication, tools, and resources according to the team’s requirements for both their project and social interactions.","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1},"end":{"line":8,"column":1}},"key":"dWjIw8HHsX"}],"key":"kW6E43SMmo"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Coordinate the development and maintenance of all the required documentation such as the organisation’s policies, participation guidelines, project charter, and information of other team members.","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"hHhDryaLEf"}],"key":"KSLCj1XeW9"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ensure that details of these resources are available for all members through a central repository, with information on how they can access them.","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1},"end":{"line":10,"column":1}},"key":"z860PVx1n0"}],"key":"DtxYNxW1pP"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Respect time differences when dealing with members across different time zones and assigning tasks. Allow a degree of flexibility as per their working situation or caring responsibilities they may have.","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"A2tTr4VbdU"}],"key":"C4Yo2RwGzn"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Schedule team meetings where everyone can share what they are working on and invite contributions and support from others in the team.","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"key":"D2sXENt1fT"}],"key":"UZpL6WNTh4"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Before the meeting, provide the meeting agenda in a shared document, preferably that can be updated by the team members in case they want to suggest a new agenda point. This document can also be used for taking notes during the event.","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1},"end":{"line":13,"column":1}},"key":"IxkJe3yVZA"}],"key":"sh7J0g8lQx"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Share minutes (and video recording when possible) to make sure that everyone is up-to-date, even those who couldn’t attend the meeting.","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"key":"Xy8UCL1gFA"}],"key":"is31lNpWF7"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Schedule regular one-on-one meetings to ensure that your team members can check-in with you, align ideas as per the project’s requirement, hold accountability for their work, and receive constructive feedback.","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"key":"cSqpmMcnU6"}],"key":"Wvj8Y6bRAq"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Create opportunities for informal interactions that can help create a friendly work environment and build a strong sense of team spirit.","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"joXVynNsDY"}],"key":"Cj6PBAHJx7"},{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Encourage and embrace diversity and a culture of collaboration.","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"p1klJ4d9gw"}],"key":"CFHw0ksPml"}],"key":"N0qMwNtCDc"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Further reading","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1},"end":{"line":19,"column":1}},"key":"RJ8GUQ6mjH"}],"identifier":"further-reading","label":"Further reading","html_id":"further-reading","implicit":true,"key":"qyBQrdm3Nt"},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"spread":false,"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":true,"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Read this post by Zapier on ","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"key":"eaUdz2